    <refsection id="Description_mdaq_pwm">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
		
		This block controls MicroDAQ PWM modules. One of three PWM modules can be selected (PWM1, PWM2, PWM3), PWM period is defined with 1us resolution, 
		'Polarity' parameters allows generate inverted PWM waveform. Block inputs range is 0-100 (duty in %). 
		
		</para>
    </refsection>
	
	<refsection id="InputOutput_mdaq_pwm">
        <title>Block Input/Output ports</title>
		<para>
		<member><para>
			input(1) - PWM A channel waveform duty
		</para></member>
		
		<member><para>
			input(2) - PWM B channel waveform duty
		</para></member>
	
		</para>
    
	</refsection>

